dcterms:description: The dataset consists of 500 manually annotated user timelines (18.7K posts) from 500 users of an online platform, specifically focusing on identifying moments of change in mood based on shared online content.
dcterms:title: Moments of Change (MoC) Dataset

dcterms:description: Talklife is a peer-to-peer network for mental health support that incorporates all the common features of social networks, providing a rich resource for computational analysis of mental health.
dcterms:title: Talklife
